{"tid":2273074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰：逾九成機師及空姐已跪，已簽新約 (明年將不獲加薪，不會獲發年終獎金)","createTime":"2020-11-05T12:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T13:56:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5f933ca8cdb54c239f74935a13be206597db4386","tid":2273074,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aw0_lf3HYA1XHUJ311yYiQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/CX-SIGN-201105-13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Faw0_lf3HYA1XHUJ311yYiQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FCX-SIGN-201105-13.jpg&h=bafab5a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】國泰航空指，逾九成機師及機艙服務員已簽署新合約。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空要求機組人員簽新合約的限期周三屆滿。國泰航空表示，有2613位機師及7346位機艙服務員已簽新約，即約98.5%機師及91.6%機艙服務員。<br />\n<br />\n至於選擇不簽新約的員工，國泰指尊重他們的決定，會提供優於勞工法例的離職方案，包括公司的退休金供款不會被對沖。離職員工亦可獲退還參與自願性特別休假計劃薪金。<br />\n<br />\n國泰又指，公司所有員工明年將不獲加薪，亦不會獲發2020年度的酌情年終獎金。"},{"pid":"3fefed92ff375b6fe2614d9c1eef6c5528beb4d9","tid":2273074,"uid":152371,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5f933ca8cdb54c239f74935a13be206597db4386","tid":2273074,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aw0_lf3HYA1XHUJ311yYiQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/CX-SIGN-201105-13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Faw0_lf3HYA1XHUJ311yYiQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FCX-SIGN-201105-13.jpg&h=bafab5a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】國泰航空指，逾九成機師及機艙服務員已簽署新合約。<b